-- ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- 20260708_dbf_p3_anon_rpc_revoke.sql
-- DB-Foundation Phase P3 (anon closure) — REVOKE EXECUTE FROM anon on public RPCs  [item ④]
--   docs/db-foundation-roadmap.md → Phase P3; database-standard.md §1–§2.
--
-- ⚠️ RED-TIER: revokes anon EXECUTE on 322 SECURITY DEFINER functions (generated from the
--   LIVE catalog: 327 anon-executable public functions minus the 5 existing §2-allowlist RPCs;
--   get_sign_document_templates is the 6th allowlist RPC, created + anon-granted in its own
--   migration). Staged for the owner's apply window. One shared Supabase — live in prod on apply.
--
-- WHAT THIS DOES (plain language):
--   These database functions were callable by the logged-out anonymous browser role. The app
--   calls them as `authenticated`; workers as service_role. This removes anon's ability to run
--   them, keeping authenticated + service_role explicitly.
--
-- MANAGED-SUPABASE NUANCE (verified — database-standard §1, Phase F): each function carries TWO
--   grants that reach anon: an explicit `anon=EXECUTE` AND PostgreSQL's built-in
--   `EXECUTE TO PUBLIC` (anon ∈ PUBLIC). BOTH are revoked — revoking anon alone leaves the PUBLIC
--   grant and anon keeps executing. `authenticated` and `service_role` hold their OWN explicit
--   grants (verified in the live proacl) and are re-GRANTed here belt-and-suspenders, so nothing
--   authenticated can regress.
--
-- KEPT ANON (§2 allowlist — deliberately absent below):
--   get_feature_flags, get_employee_page_access (login/devLogin bootstrap);
--   get_crm_build_progress (public /status); upsert_lead_from_form (public form-submit — worker
--   path today, may be tightened later per §2's note now that no browser caller is confirmed);
--   get_sign_request_by_token + get_sign_document_templates (public e-sign).
--
-- ROLLBACK: see the commented "-- ROLLBACK" block at the foot (re-GRANTs anon on all 322).
-- ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

